<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.3.9">
<l>ōyu mūppu piṟappiṟap puppiṇi</l>
<l>vīyu māṟucey vāṉṟiru vēṅkaṭat</l>
<l>tāya ṉāṇmala rāmaṭit tāmarai</l>
<l>vāyuḷ ḷummaṉat tuḷḷumvaip pārkaṭkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Old age, birth, dying [and] sickness will come to an end</l>
<l>for those who place in [their] mouths and in [their] minds</l>
<l>the foot lotuses that are day-[fresh] blossoms of the cowherd</l>
<l>from sacred Vēṅkaṭam, the one who makes a way [for them] to perish.</l>

      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
